---
title: Turkey and Spinach Rigatoni with Chili Flakes
description: Ground turkey spiced with Italian seasonings and chili flakes is the star of this pasta, but we also love the sauce, made with spinach and crushed tomatoes tossed with cream. Don't forget about the perfectly al dente rigatoni!

